author: @charmgrc9611
text:
Dear SEVENTEEN,
I hope this letter finds you well. I just wanted to take a moment to express my admiration for you and all that you do. You have been a huge source of inspiration for me, and I cannot thank you enough for the impact that you have had on my life.
I first discovered you when I was going through a difficult time in my life. Your music spoke to me in a way that nothing else did, and it was like you were able to put into words exactly what I was feeling. Your lyrics have helped me through so many tough times, and for that, I will always be grateful.
But it's not just your music that I admire. Your dedication to your fans is truly remarkable. You take the time to interact with us on social media, and your meet and greets always leave us feeling like we are more than just fans, but friends.
I have been fortunate enough to attend some of your concerts, and they are truly magical. The energy that you bring to the stage is contagious, and it's clear that you genuinely love what you do.
I know that being an idol comes with its own set of challenges, and I cannot imagine how difficult it must be to balance your personal life with your career. But please know that your fans love and support you no matter what.
Thank you for all that you do, SEVENTEEN. Keep being the amazing person that you are, and know that you have a fan for life.
Always, Carat (Charm)ğŸ¯ğŸ’ğŸ’™ğŸ’“

author: @harito_1004
text: Happy Birthday to Kwon Soonyoung, a wonderful being that I never asked for, the universe simply gave it to me as a gift, it wanted to fill my soul, I wanted to bring back my emotions, my dreams, my "I". I used to say that I didn't have an ideal type of guy because I lacked imagination, self love, standards, faith, my mind was just lacking until I came to understand that "I DESERVE EVERYTHING GOOD" and yes... I'm talking about Kwon Soonyoung, the boy who has given me the universe, my favorite gift from the universe and beings of light, when I saw it for the first time my mind said... Wow "this must be love at second sight" since we all have the first one but with him it was something different. This boy with an angelic face, celestial beauty, slanted eyes 10:10 and a free, charismatic and optimistic spirit magically became my ideal type of boy, all of him and when I say EVERYTHING it is that I love every inch and atom that make up her body, her way of dressing, dancing, acting, singing, speaking, loving, treating others with such respect, humility, kindness and admiration is something that still does not fit in my head. It is so sweet, so beautiful that my soul cries with gratitude for the marvelous art that Father God has created, it is everything I never imagined loving. For kwon I not only feel love but also admiration, respect, value, inspiration, his being is priceless, he is so valuable that I would like to place him in a crystal ball to protect him from all the negative things but I remember that he comes from another galaxy, he is someone strong , with a wild and powerful soul because it is my universe. I'm always grateful to this cute boy for making my days special and magical, beautiful and valuable, I know it's okay because God hears my requests, tears, supplications and gratitude, my vibes keep him safe, I know, I'm sorry... I love you boy of a thousand colors who has been with me in my healing process, has brought me back to life and above all has embraced my mistakes, failures and weaknesses to turn them into the opposite, I love you universe boy. â™¡
